 the core-shell Au@SiO 2 composite. As shown in Figure 1a, Au@SiO 2 spheres having a uniform diameter of about 120 nm and containing only one Au nanoparticle at the center of each sphere have been successfully prepared through careful control over hydrolysis [ Ã ] Prof.},
