m the TOF spectra) have been determined. Thermal effects can be safely excluded [12]. Figure 1 shows the irradiation-induced decay of the desorption signal of neutral NO vs total number of impinged photons, comparing ns (3.5 eV, p-polarized) and fs (3.},
